Lyrics: 
Lu hai Manungkotaima mero dil basyo lali othaimaa.
Lu hai manung kotaima najar nalagau lali othaima.

Pirati lam na ta Saili ghumna lai jamna ta.
Pirati launna ma Saila ekdine pauna sa.

Oi hoi damauli katesi madiko pool hitaiko mayalai gulab ko phool.

Ghara mero rukumai timi Mam pareu ukhumai.
Ghar mero tanahu ho launa ke bhanam bhanam bho.

Na rup maa khot timro sundar gulabi otha timro.
Ke hereu tesari o kho laaj lagyo besari.

O hoi marsyandi salala paniko bhel kisimai raichha ni mayako khel.

Tan ramro Mam ramro timi lajauda jhan ramro.
Jiu pani kasilo timro muharai hasilo.

Ke socheu bhanata timle paraichheu Manata.
Ma ta gurung ki chhori ho mero khyalmai dil chori bho.

snippet.title: YABI - AJAVOLI ft. BLUESSS ( OFFICIAL AUDIO )
snippet.description:
Track 2 from the BOOMERANG mixtape, ‚ÄúAjavoli‚Äù featuring Bluesss, delivers smooth melodies and emotional storytelling. A song about love, reflection, and feelings that never fade, this track shows a softer but powerful side of Yabi The Goat.


Heartfelt thanks to RACHANA DAHAL  for the beautiful back vocals. Your voice added depth, emotion, and soul to this track. Truly grateful for your support and talent.

‚ÄòAjavoli‚Äô is inspired by the original song by Sudip Giri. The emotions, melody, and soul of the original track sparked a new creative direction, allowing this version to reflect personal experiences while honoring the essence and artistry of the original work. Much respect to Sudip Giri for the inspiration.‚Äù


‚Ñó 2026 Yabi The Goat. All rights reserved. Unauthorized use or re-upload of this content is prohibited.

snippet.title: Sajjan Raj Vaidya - Patra [Official Release]
snippet.description:
Letters within letters to let her know, that in all of my loving she is all I‚Äôve known. For when the night falls, and thoughts surround you and force a conversation, you realise neither time nor space can create distance from her of any kind. And so each day becomes a mere addition to how long you‚Äôve spent missing her. Each morning becomes a promise to face another night, once more, belonging to only her.
___________________________________________

About "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara"
"Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" is a popular Nepali folk song that originates from the Lamjung district of Nepal. It is a lively and upbeat song that is typically sung and danced to during festivals and social gatherings.

The lyrics of the song are in the Nepali language and describe the beauty of the Lamjung district's natural scenery, including the mountains, rivers, and forests. The song also celebrates the joy and happiness of the people living in Lamjung and their culture and traditions.

The musical arrangement of "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" typically features traditional Nepali instruments such as the madal (a type of drum), tungna (a stringed instrument), and sarangi (a bowed instrument). The song has a catchy melody and rhythm that are easy to dance along to.

Over time, "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" has become a beloved Nepali folk song that is popular across the country and is often performed by musicians and dancers at cultural events and festivals.

About "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara"
"Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" is a popular Nepali folk song that originates from the Lamjung district of Nepal. It is a lively and upbeat song that is typically sung and danced to during festivals and social gatherings.

The lyrics of the song are in the Nepali language and describe the beauty of the Lamjung district's natural scenery, including the mountains, rivers, and forests. The song also celebrates the joy and happiness of the people living in Lamjung and their culture and traditions.

The musical arrangement of "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" typically features traditional Nepali instruments such as the madal (a type of drum), tungna (a stringed instrument), and sarangi (a bowed instrument). The song has a catchy melody and rhythm that are easy to dance along to.

Over time, "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" has become a beloved Nepali folk song that is popular across the country and is often performed by musicians and dancers at cultural events and festivals.

About "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara"
"Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" is a popular Nepali folk song that originates from the Lamjung district of Nepal. It is a lively and upbeat song that is typically sung and danced to during festivals and social gatherings.

The lyrics of the song are in the Nepali language and describe the beauty of the Lamjung district's natural scenery, including the mountains, rivers, and forests. The song also celebrates the joy and happiness of the people living in Lamjung and their culture and traditions.

The musical arrangement of "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" typically features traditional Nepali instruments such as the madal (a type of drum), tungna (a stringed instrument), and sarangi (a bowed instrument). The song has a catchy melody and rhythm that are easy to dance along to.

Over time, "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" has become a beloved Nepali folk song that is popular across the country and is often performed by musicians and dancers at cultural events and festivals.

snippet.title: Rze- Gimme The Loot x Manas Ghale(PROD BY SHIGU)
snippet.description:
BLACKHOUSEMOB presents Gimme The Loot From The album RZE (RUTHLESS ZONE)

By yourz truly RZE

This video is a music video for the song "Gimme The Loot" by RZE and Manash Ghale, produced by Shigu. The song is from RZE's album "RUTHLESS ZONE." The video features RZE and Manash Ghale performing the song, which has a hip-hop/rap style with lyrics about street life and asserting dominance (0:42-1:02, 1:31-1:53). The phrase "Give me the loot" is a prominent hook throughout the song (1:16-1:28, 2:16-2:20, 3:23-3:34). The video credits Jenish Maharjan as the director, Risheek Pradhan as the creative director, and features visuals by NFTP.

Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Team of the Year is Here! RIP TOTY?
snippet.description:
The new Team of the Year (TOTY) event is here, and it is a disaster. Today, I expose everything wrong with FC Mobile 26.

In this video, I break down why the New Draft System is a scam and why the removal of Store Packs destroys the Free-to-Play (F2P) experience. I also expose the terrible exchange rates for Phase 2 Tokens and Market Pick Tokens (only 5 tokens for a 115 OVR?!).

To prove my point, I spend my 10 Free Draft Vouchers on few different accounts and show you the pack probabilities. I am officially starting the #FixFCMobileTOTY movement. Until EA Sports fixes these issues, I will not be spending any FC Points or Gems.

en.title: Team of the Year is Here! RIP TOTY?
en.description:
The new Team of the Year (TOTY) event is here, and it is a disaster. Today, I expose everything wrong with FC Mobile 26.

In this video, I break down why the New Draft System is a scam and why the removal of Store Packs destroys the Free-to-Play (F2P) experience. I also expose the terrible exchange rates for Phase 2 Tokens and Market Pick Tokens (only 5 tokens for a 115 OVR?!).

To prove my point, I spend my 10 Free Draft Vouchers on few different accounts and show you the pack probabilities. I am officially starting the #FixFCMobileTOTY movement. Until EA Sports fixes these issues, I will not be spending any FC Points or Gems.
